    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to someone but it feels so robotic. like a script. everything is just so heavy and empty lately, and talking doesn't change the fact that nothing actually matters. it's just a cycle of existing for no reason. don't you think it's weird how much we struggle just to stay in a world that doesn't care if we're here or not?",
